ly before the day the application is made.\r\n(2) Subclause (1) does not apply to an applicant who meets the requirements of clause\r\n485.232, 485.233, 485.234 or 485.235.\r\nWhen a Temporary Graduate (Subclass 485) visa is lodged, it must be accompanied by\r\nevidence that the applicant has applied for an Australian Federal Police check during the 12\r\nmonths immediately before the day the application is made.\r\nAssessment\r\nOn 9 March 2025 the applicant lodged an application for a (Post-Higher Education Work\r\nstream) (Subclass 485) visa. The applicant declared Yes to:\r\nHave you and all persons included in this application who are 16 years of age or over,\r\napplied in the last 12 months to the Australian Federal Police for a check of criminal records?\r\nThe applicant provided the official invoice from the Australian Federal Police (AFP) as\r\nsupporting evidence at the time of their application.\r\nOn 28 April 2025, the application was assessed by the delegate based on the evidence\r\nprovided with their application. The evidence provided specifies that the application for the\r\nAustralian Federal Police check was lodged on 9 March 2025, which is the same day the\r\nTemporary Graduate (subclass 485) visa was lodged.\r\nAs the applicant did not apply for an Australian Federal Police clearance during the\r\n12 months immediately before the day they lodged their visa application, I find the applicant\r\ndoes not satisfy the requirements of Regulation 485.213.\r\nDecision\r\nAs clause 485.213 is not met by the applicant, I find the criteria for the grant of a Temporary\r\nGraduate (Post Higher Education Work) visa in the Post-Higher Education Work stream are\r\nnot met by the applicant, and thus the applicant does not meet the criteria for the grant of a\r\nTemporary Graduate (Post Higher Education Work) visa. I therefore find the criteria for the\r\ngrant of a Temporary Graduate visa are not met by the applicant.\r\nTherefore, I refuse the application by the applicant for a Temporary Graduate visa.\r\nAs the application has been assessed as not meeting the requirements of clause 485.213, I\r\nhave not assessed the application further against the requirements of this subclass.\"\r\n\r\nCould you please have a call with me and let me know. I am really bad place and feeling completely lost.</span> <p class=\"text-semi-light-grey col-v-1\">@ 10:30 AM-11:00 AM</p></div>', '2025-04-29 19:58:53', '2025-04-29 19:58:53', 'scheduled an paid appointment', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
